docs.name: Trouble Brewing II - Yoshito Sekigawa - Code Name S.T.E.A.M.
docs.description:
Nintendo made a game where Abraham Lincoln recruited folklore hero's and pitted them against aliens. That sounds weird, but some great tracks came out of it! That's why I'm taking the time to map out a few. This is the in-game version of the most well known track "Trouble Brewing II" which you may partially recognize from Super Smash Bros Ultimate. Hope you enjoy!

Note, this song is high energy throughout, there wont be many break points especially in higher difficulties.

docs.name: Gareth Coker - Naru, Embracing the Light
docs.description:
From the Ori and the Blind Forest OST!

Chroma map that contains 6K+ Events!

NOTE FOR QUEST USERS: This map utilizes the Billie environment which, as of now (2/7/2022), does not work with the current version mods can run on for Quest. If Quest users attempt to play this map, the BPM will change upon the first lighting event and notes.

Shoutout to Ori Jinn!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJamlTnIaQg

Difficulties: Expert+ (Ori) | Expert (Naru)
NPS (Ori): 2.45
NPS (Naru): 1.64
BPM: 174
Length: 1:24
